1769 void StatementBinder::Visit(TryStatementNode& tryStatementNode)
1770 {
1771     BoundTryStatement* boundTryStatement = new BoundTryStatement(module, tryStatementNode.GetSpan());
1772     tryStatementNode.TryBlock()->Accept(*this);
1773     boundTryStatement->SetTryBlock(std::move(statement));
1774     int n = tryStatementNode.Catches().Count();
1775     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
1776     {
1777         CatchNode* catchNode = tryStatementNode.Catches()[i];
1778         catchNode->Accept(*this);
1779         BoundStatement* s = statement.release();
1780         Assert(s->GetBoundNodeType() == BoundNodeType::boundCatchStatement, "catch statement expected");
1781         BoundCatchStatement* catchStatement = static_cast<BoundCatchStatement*>(s);
1782         boundTryStatement->AddCatch(std::unique_ptr<BoundCatchStatement>(catchStatement));
1783     }
1784     AddStatement(boundTryStatement);
1785 }
1786 
1787 void StatementBinder::Visit(CatchNode& catchNode)
1788 {
1789     bool prevInsideCatch = insideCatch;
1790     insideCatch = true;
1791     Span span;
1792     if (GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::llvm)
1793     {
1794         span = catchNode.GetSpan();
1795     }
1796     std::unique_ptr<BoundCatchStatement> boundCatchStatement(new BoundCatchStatement(module, span));
1797     TypeSymbol* catchedType = ResolveType(catchNode.TypeExpr(), boundCompileUnit, containerScope);
1798     boundCatchStatement->SetCatchedType(catchedType);
1799     boundCatchStatement->SetCatchedTypeUuidId(boundCompileUnit.Install(catchedType->BaseType()->TypeId()));
1800     LocalVariableSymbol* catchVar = nullptr;
1801     if (catchNode.Id())
1802     {
1803         Symbol* symbol = symbolTable.GetSymbol(catchNode.Id());
1804         Assert(symbol->GetSymbolType() == SymbolType::localVariableSymbol, "local variable symbol expected");
1805         catchVar = static_cast<LocalVariableSymbol*>(symbol);
1806         boundCatchStatement->SetCatchVar(catchVar);
1807         currentFunction->GetFunctionSymbol()->AddLocalVariable(catchVar);
1808     }
1809     CompoundStatementNode handlerBlock(catchNode.CatchBlock()->BeginBraceSpan());
1810     handlerBlock.SetBeginBraceSpan(catchNode.CatchBlock()->BeginBraceSpan());
1811     handlerBlock.SetEndBraceSpan(catchNode.CatchBlock()->EndBraceSpan());
1812     handlerBlock.SetParent(catchNode.Parent());
1813     if (GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::llvm || GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::cmcpp)
1814     {
1815         ConstructionStatementNode* getExceptionAddr = new ConstructionStatementNode(span, new PointerNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"void")), new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exceptionAddr"));
1816         getExceptionAddr->AddArgument(new InvokeNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"RtGetException")));
1817         handlerBlock.AddStatement(getExceptionAddr);
1818     }
1819     else if (GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::cmsx)
1820     {
1821         ConstructionStatementNode* getExceptionAddr = new ConstructionStatementNode(span, new PointerNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"void")), new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exceptionAddr"));
1822         getExceptionAddr->AddArgument(new InvokeNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"do_catch")));
1823         handlerBlock.AddStatement(getExceptionAddr);
1824     }
1825     PointerNode exceptionPtrTypeNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, catchedType->BaseType()->FullName()));
1826     CloneContext cloneContext;
1827     SpanMapper spanMapper;
1828     cloneContext.SetSpanMapper(&spanMapper);
1829     ConstructionStatementNode* constructExceptionPtr = new ConstructionStatementNode(span, exceptionPtrTypeNode.Clone(cloneContext), new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exceptionPtr"));
1830     constructExceptionPtr->AddArgument(new CastNode(span, exceptionPtrTypeNode.Clone(cloneContext), new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exceptionAddr")));
1831     handlerBlock.AddStatement(constructExceptionPtr);
1832     TemplateIdNode* uniquePtrNode = new TemplateIdNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"UniquePtr"));
1833     uniquePtrNode->AddTemplateArgument(new IdentifierNode(span, catchedType->BaseType()->FullName()));
1834     ConstructionStatementNode* constructUniquePtrException = new ConstructionStatementNode(span, uniquePtrNode, new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exPtr"));
1835     constructUniquePtrException->AddArgument(new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exceptionPtr"));
1836     handlerBlock.AddStatement(constructUniquePtrException);
1837     if (catchVar)
1838     {
1839         ConstructionStatementNode* setExceptionVar = new ConstructionStatementNode(span, catchNode.TypeExpr()->Clone(cloneContext), static_cast<IdentifierNode*>(catchNode.Id()->Clone(cloneContext)));
1840         setExceptionVar->AddArgument(new DerefNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exPtr")));
1841         handlerBlock.AddStatement(setExceptionVar);
1842     }
1843     handlerBlock.AddStatement(static_cast<StatementNode*>(catchNode.CatchBlock()->Clone(cloneContext)));
1844     symbolTable.BeginContainer(containerScope->Container());
1845     SymbolCreatorVisitor symbolCreatorVisitor(symbolTable);
1846     handlerBlock.Accept(symbolCreatorVisitor);
1847     symbolTable.EndContainer();
1848     TypeBinder typeBinder(boundCompileUnit);
1849     typeBinder.SetContainerScope(containerScope);
1850     typeBinder.SetCurrentFunctionSymbol(currentFunction->GetFunctionSymbol());
1851     handlerBlock.Accept(typeBinder);
1852     handlerBlock.Accept(*this);
1853     boundCatchStatement->SetCatchBlock(std::move(statement));
1854     AddStatement(boundCatchStatement.release());
1855     insideCatch = prevInsideCatch;
1856 }

1858 void StatementBinder::Visit(AssertStatementNode& assertStatementNode)
1859 {
1860     if (!module)
1861     {
1862         throw std::runtime_error("module not set");
1863     }
1864     bool unitTesting = GetGlobalFlag(GlobalFlags::unitTest) && InUnitTest();
1865     bool unitTestAssertion = false;
1866     if (unitTesting)
1867     {
1868         FunctionSymbol* functionSymbol = currentFunction->GetFunctionSymbol();
1869         Node* node = symbolTable.GetNodeNoThrow(functionSymbol);
1870         if (node)
1871         {
1872             if (node->GetNodeType() == NodeType::functionNode)
1873             {
1874                 FunctionNode* functionNode = static_cast<FunctionNode*>(node);
1875                 if ((functionNode->GetSpecifiers() & Specifiers::unit_test_) != Specifiers::none)
1876                 {
1877                     unitTestAssertion = true;
1878                 }
1879             }
1880         }
1881     }
1882     if (unitTestAssertion)
1883     {
1884         int32_t assertionLineNumber = assertStatementNode.GetSpan().line;
1885         int32_t assertionIndex = GetNextUnitTestAssertionNumber();
1886         AddAssertionLineNumber(assertionLineNumber);
1887         InvokeNode* invokeSetUnitTestAssertionResult = new InvokeNode(assertStatementNode.GetSpan(), new IdentifierNode(assertStatementNode.GetSpan(), U"RtSetUnitTestAssertionResult"));
1888         invokeSetUnitTestAssertionResult->AddArgument(new IntLiteralNode(assertStatementNode.GetSpan(), assertionIndex));
1889         CloneContext cloneContext;
1890         SpanMapper spanMapper;
1891         cloneContext.SetSpanMapper(&spanMapper);
1892         invokeSetUnitTestAssertionResult->AddArgument(assertStatementNode.AssertExpr()->Clone(cloneContext));
1893         invokeSetUnitTestAssertionResult->AddArgument(new IntLiteralNode(assertStatementNode.GetSpan(), assertionLineNumber));
1894         ExpressionStatementNode setUnitTestAssertionResult(assertStatementNode.GetSpan(), invokeSetUnitTestAssertionResult);
1895         symbolTable.BeginContainer(containerScope->Container());
1896         SymbolCreatorVisitor symbolCreatorVisitor(symbolTable);
1897         setUnitTestAssertionResult.Accept(symbolCreatorVisitor);
1898         symbolTable.EndContainer();
1899         TypeBinder typeBinder(boundCompileUnit);
1900         typeBinder.SetContainerScope(containerScope);
1901         typeBinder.SetCurrentFunctionSymbol(currentFunction->GetFunctionSymbol());
1902         setUnitTestAssertionResult.Accept(typeBinder);
1903         setUnitTestAssertionResult.Accept(*this);
1904     }
1905     else
1906     {
1907         if (GetGlobalFlag(GlobalFlags::release))
1908         {
1909             AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, assertStatementNode.GetSpan()));
1910         }
1911         else
1912         {
1913             std::vector<FunctionScopeLookup> lookups;
1914             lookups.push_back(FunctionScopeLookup(ScopeLookup::this_and_base_and_parent, symbolTable.GlobalNs().GetContainerScope()));
1915             std::vector<std::std::unique_ptr<BoundExpression>>arguments;
1916             TypeSymbol* constCharPtrType = symbolTable.GetTypeByName(U"char")->AddConst(Span())->AddPointer(Span());
1917             arguments.push_back(std::unique_ptr<BoundExpression>(new BoundLiteral(module, std::unique_ptr<Value>(new StringValue(Span(), 
1918                 boundCompileUnit.Install(assertStatementNode.AssertExpr()->ToString()), assertStatementNode.AssertExpr()->ToString())), constCharPtrType)));
1919             arguments.push_back(std::unique_ptr<BoundExpression>(new BoundLiteral(module, std::unique_ptr<Value>(new StringValue(Span(), 
1920                 boundCompileUnit.Install(ToUtf8(currentFunction->GetFunctionSymbol()->FullName())), ToUtf8(currentFunction->GetFunctionSymbol()->FullName()))), constCharPtrType)));
1921             arguments.push_back(std::unique_ptr<BoundExpression>(new BoundLiteral(module, std::unique_ptr<Value>(new StringValue(Span(), 
1922                 boundCompileUnit.Install(module->GetFilePath(assertStatementNode.GetSpan().fileIndex)), module->GetFilePath(assertStatementNode.GetSpan().fileIndex))), constCharPtrType)));
1923             arguments.push_back(std::unique_ptr<BoundExpression>(new BoundLiteral(module, std::unique_ptr<Value>(new IntValue(Span(), 
1924                 assertStatementNode.GetSpan().line)), symbolTable.GetTypeByName(U"int"))));
1925             std::unique_ptr<BoundExpression> assertExpression = BindExpression(assertStatementNode.AssertExpr(), boundCompileUnit, currentFunction, containerScope, this);
1926             const char32_t* failAssertionFunctionName = U"";
1927             if (GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::llvm || GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::cmcpp)
1928             {
1929                 failAssertionFunctionName = U"RtFailAssertion";
1930             }
1931             else if (GetBackEnd() == BackEnd::cmsx)
1932             {
1933                 failAssertionFunctionName = U"System.FailAssertion";
1934             }
1935             std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement> emptyStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, Span()));
1936             emptyStatement->SetIgnoreNode();
1937             std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement> failAssertionStatement(
1938                 new BoundExpressionStatement(module, ResolveOverload(failAssertionFunctionName, containerScope, lookups, arguments, 
1939                     boundCompileUnit, currentFunction, Span()), Span()));
1940             failAssertionStatement->SetIgnoreNode();
1941             std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement> ifStatement(new BoundIfStatement(module, assertStatementNode.GetSpan(), std::move(assertExpression), 
1942                 std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement>(emptyStatement.release()), 
1943                 std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement>(failAssertionStatement.release())));
1944             ifStatement->SetAssertNode();
1945             AddStatement(ifStatement.release());
1946         }
1947     }
1948 }

1991 void StatementBinder::Visit(ConditionalCompilationStatementNode& conditionalCompilationStatementNode)
1992 {
1993     conditionalCompilationStatementNode.IfPart()->Accept(*this);
1994     bool defined = conditionalCompilationStack.top();
1995     conditionalCompilationStack.pop();
1996     if (defined)
1997     {
1998         int n = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.IfPart()->Statements().Count();
1999         if (n > 0)
2000         {
2001             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
2002             {
2003                 StatementNode* statement = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.IfPart()->Statements()[i];
2004                 statement->Accept(*this);
2005             }
2006         }
2007         else
2008         {
2009             AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
2010         }
2011     }
2012     else
2013     {
2014         bool executed = false;
2015         int n = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.ElifParts().Count();
2016         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
2017         {
2018             ConditionalCompilationPartNode* elifPart = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.ElifParts()[i];
2019             elifPart->Accept(*this);
2020             bool defined = conditionalCompilationStack.top();
2021             conditionalCompilationStack.pop();
2022             if (defined)
2023             {
2024                 int n = elifPart->Statements().Count();
2025                 if (n > 0)
2026                 {
2027                     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
2028                     {
2029                         StatementNode* statement = elifPart->Statements()[i];
2030                         statement->Accept(*this);
2031                     }
2032                 }
2033                 else
2034                 {
2035                     AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
2036                 }
2037                 executed = true;
2038                 break;
2039             }
2040         }
2041         if (!executed)
2042         {
2043             ConditionalCompilationPartNode* elsePart = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.ElsePart();
2044             if (elsePart)
2045             {
2046                 int n = elsePart->Statements().Count();
2047                 if (n > 0)
2048                 {
2049                     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
2050                     {
2051                         StatementNode* statement = elsePart->Statements()[i];
2052                         statement->Accept(*this);
2053                     }
2054                 }
2055                 else
2056                 {
2057                     AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
2058                 }
2059             }
2060             else
2061             {
2062                 AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
2063             }
2064         }
2065     }
2066 }

2106 void StatementBinder::AddStatement(BoundStatement* boundStatement)
2107 {
2108     if (postfix)
2109     {
2110         boundStatement->SetPostfix();
2111     }
2112     if (statement)
2113     {
2114         if (statement->Postfix())
2115         {
2116             BoundSequenceStatement* sequenceStatement = new BoundSequenceStatement(module, boundStatement->GetSpan(), std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement>(boundStatement), std::move(statement));
2117             boundStatement = sequenceStatement;
2118         }
2119         else
2120         {
2121             BoundSequenceStatement* sequenceStatement = new BoundSequenceStatement(module, boundStatement->GetSpan(), std::move(statement), std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement>(boundStatement));
2122             boundStatement = sequenceStatement;
2123         }
2124         if (postfix)
2125         {
2126             boundStatement->SetPostfix();
2127         }
2128     }
2129     statement.reset(boundStatement);
2130 }
